                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "No.JS is an HTML-first reactive framework that lets you build dynamic web applications using just HTML attributes. No build step required, no virtual DOM, no compilation — just drop in a script tag and start building.",
